# AI WorkMate Rules

Before editing this repository, read:

- `AGENTS.md`
- `docs/rules/engineering-rules.md`
- `docs/rules/frontend-rules.md` for `frontend/**`
- `docs/rules/backend-rules.md` for `backend/**`
- `docs/rules/agent-rules.md` for AI/RAG/Agent work

Use these skills when relevant:

- `docs/skills/frontend-design-skill.md`
- `docs/skills/motion-skill.md`
- `docs/skills/backend-engineering-skill.md`
- `docs/skills/agent-engineering-skill.md`

Core requirements:

- Keep changes scoped.
- Do not leak secrets.
- Preserve frontend/backend API contracts.
- Validate with `npm run lint`, `npm run build`, or `mvn test` when applicable.
- Use Conventional Commits for commit messages.
